245
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,840
Kung gayon, kailangan nating humanap ng paraan
para mapataas ang ating tsansa.

246
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,600
May ideya ka?

247
00:14:53,390 --> 00:14:54,510
Ikapitong Lola,

248
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:55,630
