286
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:12,550
Puro kalokohan ang sinasabi mo.

287
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:13,670
Zhan Dongtu...

288
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:15,600
Ang iyong lipstick.

289
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:18,550
Mr. Dongtie

290
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,950
