296
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:35,960
Tama si Zhen.

297
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:38,720
Dahil mayroon ka nang plano sa isip,

298
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:40,670
Aalis ako

299
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:43,960
