Ngayong nandito na ako,

311
00:17:19,270 --> 00:17:21,329
Hindi mo ba ako imbitahan para sa isang tasa ng tsaa?

312
00:17:22,109 --> 00:17:23,640
Dahil kailangan mo ang aking pabor,

313
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:25,349
Natural lang na may masarap akong tsaa na iregalo sa iyo.

314
00:17:25,349 --> 00:17:26,210
Pumasok ka.

315
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,480
Salamat.

316
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:29,550
Ginoong He, magtimpla ka ng tsaa.

317
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:30,880
Sige, Guro.

318
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:42,630
Binibining Li Zhen, maupo po kayo.

319
00:17:43,070 --> 00:17:44,070
Sofa pala iyon.

320
