340
00:18:55,110 --> 00:18:55,920
Miss Li Zhen,

341
00:18:56,550 --> 00:18:59,720
Ano ba talaga ang pakialam mo
sa akin ngayon?

342
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:05,480
Napakatalino mo, Master Qi.

343
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:07,350
Dumating ako ngayon

344
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:10,400
