349
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,070
Kaya, gusto kong...

350
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:24,850
Ang pamilyang Tian?

351
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,680
Ginawa ba nila

352
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:30,270
