415
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:43,720
Pangatlong Lolo, aalis na ako.

416
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:44,750
Teka.

417
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:49,240
Napakalaki ng Bundok Qiyun.

418
00:22:49,270 --> 00:22:50,750
