452
00:24:59,750 --> 00:25:01,550
Napakarami mong alam.

453
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:04,830
Kung hindi mo mamasamain,

454
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:07,400
Gusto mo bang sumama sa akin?

455
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,640
Bundok Qiyun

456
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:13,110
