457
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:16,270
Maaaring magkaroon ng abala
kung pupunta ka nang mag-isa.

458
00:25:16,270 --> 00:25:19,480
Kung tayo'y sasama, maaalagaan natin
ang isa't isa sa daan.

459
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:20,720
Ano sa tingin mo?

460
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:26,550
Tara na.

461
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:31,920
Tatay.

462
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:33,270
Tumakbo nang mas mabilis.

463
00:25:34,750 --> 00:25:36,270
Tatay, pagod na ako.

464
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:37,600
Gusto ko ng piggyback ride.

465
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:41,310
Daddy, bilisan mo nang kaunti.

466
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:44,440
Sige, kumapit ka nang mahigpit.

467
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:53,720
Anong meron?

468
00:25:56,070 --> 00:25:56,720
Wala.

469
00:25:58,030 --> 00:25:59,360
Naisip ko lang ang tatay ko.

470
00:25:59,590 --> 00:26:00,720
Noong bata pa ako,

471
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:02,540
dadalhin ako ng tatay ko nang ganito

472
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:05,000
at maglakad sa arkong ito.

473
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:09,720
Nabalitaan ko na ang tungkol sa iyong ama,

474
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:14,440
