643
00:33:56,590 --> 00:33:58,160
Parang pumasok ka sa isang painting.

644
00:33:58,160 --> 00:34:01,270
Tunay ngang pinagpala ang Bundok Qiyun

645
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:02,870
